{"tid":471487,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"本地筍工推介睇電視7日袋$20000！","createTime":"2017-11-17T09:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T06:35:42.000Z","uid":153034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"57ff1e80260f2e9474b285c2cca30a8bbcf1d8dd","tid":471487,"uid":153034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/204404/本地筍工推介睇電視7日袋-20000-符合3個條件即可報名/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F204404%2F%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%8D%E5%B7%A5%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B%E7%9D%87%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%967%E6%97%A5%E8%A2%8B-20000-%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%883%E5%80%8B%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D%2F1&d=RvLaCvAG7Ymj75KR85LFNBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=7b2dc3de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/204404/本地筍工推介睇電視7日袋-20000-符合3個條件即可報名/1</a><br />\n<br />\n本地筍工推介睇電視7日袋$20000！符合3個條件即可報名<br />\n不要常常羨慕外國推出的筍工，今次機會嚟啦！近日本地公司推出一份筍工，在社交網站Facebook公開招聘「電視體驗員」，尋找一位願意安坐在指定地點睇電視的精英。工作7日，便可賺到$20,000，而且工作期間可以享有「Pantry放題」福利，非常吸引。<br />\n<br />\n至於入職要求，主要有3大條件，第一就是視覺和聽覺正常；第二是雙眼視野角度大於188度；第三是能長時間安坐。工作沒有特別的學歷要求，只要中學程度，能書寫簡單中、英文便可，亦無須工作經驗。不過懂得接駁遊戲機、電腦者更佳。<br />\n<br />\n「電視體驗員」的主要職責為測試電視各種特性，其中包括：清理包裝材料、插電線、追台方便程度。另外亦要測試電視是否有鬼影、噪點、聲音、遙控器手感。<br />\n<br />\n除了睇電視，亦要測試電視跟遊戲機、應用程式的配合程度。體驗售後服務，網上填寫保養單。"},{"pid":"c31d5eadf8a3c19e411800a7d994db2217e6e1f4","tid":471487,"uid":17353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:08:16.000Z","msg":"樓主訓左一日？"},{"pid":"2bd6b2462206108bbb787a85e7699b30db0b7597","tid":471487,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"188度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n萬中無一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f2706aba28686fec432b68b2ef6624798c79d9","tid":471487,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:35:28.000Z","msg":"睇七日七夜亞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b153a926267e9f6153c3fdb1b121dc7a30c1a8d1","tid":471487,"uid":153034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>188度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n萬中無一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話扭你條頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c230ed70357790f87c94d12e283c16860162433","tid":471487,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"請1個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  博宣傳"},{"pid":"010bf6b4854fe8e5aa29c6458d066fbb951dc5d1","tid":471487,"uid":153034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請1個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  博宣傳</blockquote><br />\n成功宣傳左佢地啲電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13990d3fe32e5bd35e2331144c227275e32b8d09","tid":471487,"uid":153034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"&lsquo;"},{"pid":"620d6e17e980445ea6de5fe2b56cc2debe24f19f","tid":471487,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:35:42.000Z","msg":"凸眼金魚？"}]}